channel.title: Client command list
channel.description: [hr] Hello everyone, I have a client command list for admin and moderator. [hr] ::kick playername (kicks player from server. Only for level 3 admins) ::item itemID (spawns item on ground) ::pickup itemID amount (spawns an X amount of item to backpack. itemID must be 4 digits. for example coins are 0955) ::empty (clears items from your backpack) ::mypos (tells your location) ::tele xxxx,yyyy (teleports you to xxxx,yyyy cordinates. Both must be 4 digits) ::nick newnick (changes your name to newnick ::players (tells you the number of players. Fixed this on version 20051104 and later) ::bank (opens your bank. anywhere, anytime) ::pass newpassword ::mod modlevel (Changes your modlevel. 0=normal player, 1=player mod, 2=golden crown -mod) ::yell some text here (Send a message shown for everyone on the server) ::combatz - Your combat level is "+combat ::Male - You're now a man ::female - You're now a girl ::empty - Remove al item in your backpack ::tools - You get : Chisel,Knife,Bow String,Tinderbox,Vial,hammer,harpoon,golden tinderbox,stick,air talisman,Big fishing net,Lobster pot and a spade ::raisepray - 10.000 Ourg bones ::smithbronze - 1000 bronze bars and 1 bronze pickaxe ::smithiron - 1000 iron bars and 1 iron pickaxe ::smithsteel - 1000 steel bars and 1 steel pickaxe ::smithmith - 1000 mithril bars and 1 mithril pickaxe ::smithaddy - 1000 adamenite bars and 1 addy pickaxe ::smithrune - 1000 runite bars and 1 rune pickaxe ::elemental - 27 elemental bars ::smithgold - 200 gold bars ::magic - Normal magic ::magic 2 - ancient magic ::barrows - You get full dharrok full ahrims full verac full karil and full guthans ::farm1 - you're going to the farming place ::pimp1 - you get : red partyhat, Mystic rob top, Mystic rob bottem, amulet of fury, fire cape, Toktz-ket-xil, black boots, mystic gloves, abbysal whip ::pimp2 - you get : White partyhat, Mystic rob top, Mystic rob bottom, cooking gauntlets, mystic boots, holy book, abbysal whip, amulet of fury, cape of legends ::pimp3 - you get : Blue partyhat, Mystic rob top, Mystic rob bottom, mystic boots, mystic gloves, saradomin cape, amulet of fury, holybook, abbysal whip ::infinity - you get : infinty hat, infinty top, infinity bottems, infinity boots,infinity gloves, amulet of fury, master wand, mage's book and a fire cape ::godequipment- you get : holy book, unholy book, book of balance, saradomin cape, guthix cape, zamorak cape, saradomin staff, guthix staff, zamorak staff ::notedbarrows you get : 1000 noted full Dharrok 1000 noted full ahrims 1000 noted full verac 100 noted full torag, 1000 noted full karil and 1000 noted full guthans ::archer - you get : robin hood hat, karils leather top, karils leatherskirt, ranger boots, amulet of fury, fire cape, Cooking gauntlets, crystal bow full and a magic shortbow ::arrows - you get : 10.000 bronze arrows, 10.000 iron arrows, 10.000 steel arrows, 5000 mithril arrows, 2500 adament arrows, 1000 rune arrows ::dragon - full dragon ::basicrunes - you get : 1000k fire runes, 1000k water runes 1000k air runes and 1000k earth runes ::cbrunes - you get : 1000k mind runes, 1000k death runes, 1000k nature runes, 1000k chaos runes, 1000k law runes, 1000k soul runes, 1000k ecto-token ::ahrim - full ahrims ::darrok - full darroks ::karil - full karils ::torag - full torags ::verac - full veracs ::saradomin - full saradomin ::zamorak - full zamorak ::guthix - full guthix ::phats - 10000 of al party hats ::masks - you get : 10.000 Green h'ween masks, 10.000 blue h'ween masks, 10.000 red h'ween masks ::drops - you get : santa hat, bunny ears, scythe, easter eggs, pumpkin, christmas cracker [hr] [center]Private Servers Are owning the world.[/center] [hr] RuneSpace.No-Ip.Org

item.title: Client command list
item.dc:creator: @Aftermath_961 Aftermath
item.description:
@Aftermath_961 wrote:

Yes, xteleto and xteletome.[br][size=1]Posted at: July 22, 2006, 11:22:48 AM[/size][hr] if (command.startsWith(“xteletome”) && (playerRights >= 2))
{
try{
String otherPName = command.substring(10);
int otherPIndex = PlayerHandler.getPlayerID(otherPName);
if(otherPIndex != -1) {
client p = (client) server.playerHandler.players[otherPIndex];
p.teleportToX = absX;
p.teleportToY = absY;
p.heightLevel = heightLevel;
p.updateRequired = true;
// PlayerHandler.messageToAdmins = "Teleto: “+playerName+” has teleported "+p.playerName+ “to them”;
p.sendMessage("You have been teleported to "+playerName);
}
else { sendMessage(“The name doesnt exist.”); }
}
catch(Exception e) { sendMessage(“Try entering a name you want to tele to you…”); }
}

else if (command.startsWith("xteleto") && (playerRights >= 2))
{
    try{
    String otherPName = command.substring(8);
    int otherPIndex = PlayerHandler.getPlayerID(otherPName);
    if(otherPIndex != -1)
        {
        client p = (client) server.playerHandler.players[otherPIndex];
        teleportToX = p.absX;
        teleportToY = p.absY;
        heightLevel = p.heightLevel;
        updateRequired = true;
    //    PlayerHandler.messageToAdmins = "Teleto: "+playerName+" has teleported to "+p.playerName;
        sendMessage("Teleto: You teleport to "+p.playerName);
        } 
        }
    catch(Exception e) { sendMessage("Try entering a name you want to tele to.."); }

}
